  <h1>PlumbTally</h1>
  <span class="app-badge">Privacy Policy</span>

  <h2>Overview</h2>
  <p>PlumbTally is a job-tracking tool for plumbers and tradespeople. We collect only the data necessary to provide the service. We do not sell your data to third parties.</p>
  <p>This policy applies to the PlumbTally mobile app (Android) and the web app at <a href="https://plumb-tally.vercel.app">plumb-tally.vercel.app</a>.</p>
  <p>Last updated: <strong>April 1, 2026</strong>.</p>

  <hr class="divider" />

  <h2>Data we collect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Account:</strong> your email address and, if you sign in with Google, your Google profile name and avatar URL.</li>
    <li><strong>Business profile:</strong> company name, phone number, address, and VAT number — entered by you, optional.</li>
    <li><strong>Projects &amp; jobs:</strong> project names, client details, line items, quantities, prices, and payment records you create.</li>
    <li><strong>Subscription status:</strong> trial start date and subscription tier.</li>
    <li><strong>Translation requests:</strong> item description text sent to our translation service when you use the auto-translate feature.</li>
  </ul>

  <hr class="divider" />

  <h2>Data we do not collect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>PDF files — generated on-device and never uploaded to our servers.</li>
    <li>Payment card details — no payment provider is integrated.</li>
    <li>Location data.</li>
    <li>Device contacts or camera.</li>
    <li>Analytics or crash telemetry beyond what Supabase logs by default.</li>
  </ul>

  <hr class="divider" />

  <h2>How we use your data</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>To authenticate you and keep your data secure.</li>
    <li>To store and sync your projects across devices.</li>
    <li>To translate item descriptions into other languages (text is sent to OpenAI via our Supabase edge function and is not stored).</li>
    <li>To manage your subscription and trial period.</li>
  </ul>

  <hr class="divider" />

  <h2>Third-party services</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Supabase</strong> — database, authentication, and edge functions. Data is stored in the EU (Frankfurt). <a href="https://supabase.com/privacy">Privacy policy</a>.</li>
    <li><strong>Google Sign-In</strong> — optional authentication provider. <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy">Privacy policy</a>.</li>
    <li><strong>OpenAI</strong> — used only for item translation. Text is processed transiently and not stored by us. <a href="https://openai.com/policies/privacy-policy">Privacy policy</a>.</li>
    <li><strong>Vercel</strong> — hosts the web app. <a href="https://vercel.com/legal/privacy-policy">Privacy policy</a>.</li>
  </ul>

  <hr class="divider" />

  <h2>Data retention</h2>
  <p>Your data is retained for as long as your account is active. When you delete your account, all data is deleted immediately and permanently — including your profile, projects, items, payments, and subscription records.</p>

  <hr class="divider" />

  <h2>Your rights</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Access:</strong> all your data is visible inside the app.</li>
    <li><strong>Deletion:</strong> delete your account at any time via Profile → Delete account, or by emailing us. See the <a href="/delete-account.html">account deletion page</a>.</li>
    <li><strong>Export:</strong> contact us to request a copy of your data.</li>
  </ul>

  <hr class="divider" />

  <h2>Security</h2>
  <p>All data is encrypted in transit (TLS). Access to your data is protected by Supabase Row-Level Security — only you can read or modify your records. The service role key is never exposed to the client.</p>

  <hr class="divider" />

  <h2>Children</h2>
  <p>PlumbTally is intended for professional use by adults. We do not knowingly collect data from anyone under 16.</p>

  <hr class="divider" />

  <h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
  <p>If we make material changes, we will update the date at the top of this page. Continued use of the app after changes constitutes acceptance.</p>

  <hr class="divider" />

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>Questions about this policy or your data:</p>
  <p><a href="mailto:support@plumbtally.app">support@plumbtally.app</a></p>

